    "name": "Buildora API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Buildora - Home Renovation Project Matching Platform.\n\n**Live Base URL:** https://web-production-afb0.up.railway.app\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Import this collection and run it with the Collection Runner\n2. Tokens and IDs are captured automatically via test scripts — no manual copy-paste needed\n3. On re-runs, the Login requests refresh tokens automatically (Register will 409, Login will succeed)\n\n**Default Admin:** admin@buildora.com / admin123\n\n**Runner order:** Auth → Projects → Proposals → Admin → Cleanup",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://web-production-afb0.up.railway.app", "type": "string" },
